# Engineering playbook (submodule)

This project mounts the shared playbook at `playbook/`.

## Before substantial work

1. Read or skim `playbook/docs/engineering/AI_PLAYBOOK.md` for stage gates and role lenses.
2. If switching tools or long sessions, maintain `HANDOFF.md` using `playbook/docs/engineering/HANDOFF.template.md`.

## Expectations

- Prefer small vertical slices with tests and rollback for user-facing changes.
- Do not duplicate long playbook text in chat; cite paths under `playbook/docs/` when giving process guidance.

## Product-specific rules

Add separate `.mdc` rules in `.cursor/rules/` for stack conventions, globs, and security (keep each rule focused).
